  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/466a22b4af853aeb9523711832c11eff.avif?t=1769786647\" width=606 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Last Will and Testament is first person adventure horror game in escape room style with lots of puzzles to solve. Fulfill the last will and find a testament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.poster.avif?t=1769786647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.webm?t=1769786647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.mp4?t=1769786647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100 Steam Achievements hidden in the haunted house! Find it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Story & voice-over</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two endings (normal and really, really secret ending)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beatiful and creepy graphic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Creepy haunted house ambience and music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Length of the game: 2-4 hours (5+ hours if you want to see the secret ending, find all collectibles etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Good optimization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hot price </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Save/load game any time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Autosave</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keyboard and mouse or gamepad controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 29 langauges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Options (graphics, disable niose/VHS effect, audio, configure controls, invert y-axis, subtitles, mouse/gamepad sensitivity etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Notes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Linux, Windows and Mac OS support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All resolution supports (21:9, Ultrawide etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam clouds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam remote (TV, phone etc.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Not for the faint-hearted</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/466a22b4af853aeb9523711832c11eff.avif?t=1769786647\" width=606 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Last Will and Testament is first person adventure horror game in escape room style with lots of puzzles to solve. Fulfill the last will and find a testament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.poster.avif?t=1769786647\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.webm?t=1769786647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2014930/extras/2db0ce569398d67a3839a9565e3fff70.mp4?t=1769786647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100 Steam Achievements hidden in the haunted house! Find it!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Story & voice-over</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two endings (normal and really, really secret ending)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beatiful and creepy graphic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Creepy haunted house ambience and music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Length of the game: 2-4 hours (5+ hours if you want to see the secret ending, find all collectibles etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Good optimization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hot price </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Save/load game any time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Autosave</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keyboard and mouse or gamepad controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 29 langauges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Options (graphics, disable niose/VHS effect, audio, configure controls, invert y-axis, subtitles, mouse/gamepad sensitivity etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Notes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Linux, Windows and Mac OS support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All resolution supports (21:9, Ultrawide etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam clouds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam remote (TV, phone etc.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Not for the faint-hearted</i></strong></p>",
